Update dbo.tempreport
Set ManagedContactMLAccountCoverage = CASE WHEN GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMSP Public Sector Corp AM' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_2
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Partner - Managed SMSP' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_2
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Partner - Regional Tele Covered' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_1
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Partner - Dynamics Managed' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_2
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMSP Corp AM' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_2
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMSP Corp TM' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_1
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMSP Public Sector Corp TM' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_1
WHEN GRSBucket = 'Partner - Telemanaged Partner' THEN Perc_AccountsManagedContact_1
ELSE 0.0000 END


select 1 abcd

--DataQuality

Update dbo.TempReport
Set DataQuality = CAST((CAST(SampleCount AS numeric(10,2)))/(CAST(FixableRejectionCount AS numeric(10,2))+CAST(SampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(5,4))
WHERE (ISNULL(FixableRejectionCount,0)+ISNULL(SampleCount,0)) > 0

--Data Quality for Managed Contacts

Update dbo.TempReport
Set DataQualityManagedContact = CAST((CAST(ManagedSampleCount AS numeric(10,2)))/(CAST(FixableRejectionCount AS numeric(10,2))+CAST(ManagedSampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(5,4))
WHERE (ISNULL(FixableRejectionCount,0)+ISNULL(ManagedSampleCount,0)) > 0


--Data Quality for Previous Wave

Update dbo.TempReport
Set ChangeDataQualityFromLastWave = CAST((CAST(PreviousWaveSampleCount AS numeric(10,2)))/(CAST(PreviousWaveFixableRejectionCount AS numeric(10,2))+CAST(PreviousWaveSampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(5,4))
WHERE (ISNULL(PreviousWaveFixableRejectionCount,0)+ISNULL(PreviousWaveSampleCount,0)) > 0


select 1 abcd

--% of Contacts from last wave under Same Segment
--35 sec
IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'Temp1' and type = 'U')
DROP TABLE dbo.Temp1


select G.CPERMListid AS GRSListID,G.SubsidiaryName,COUNT(1) AS PreviousSample into dbo.Temp1 from dbo.CPERM_Prev_Sample G with(nolock)
INNER JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_GRSList] L with(nolock)
ON G.CPERMListid = L.GRSListId
INNER JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[vw_Mst_Geography] Geo with(nolock)
ON G.SubsidiaryName = Geo.SubsidiaryName
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Scorecard] S with(nolock)
ON G.CPERMListid = S.GrslistId AND Geo.SubsidiaryId = ISNULL(S.SubsidiaryId,0) AND G.Contactid = S.ContactNumber
WHERE S.RejectionCount = 0 and 1=1----Need to ask
GROUP BY G.CPERMListid,G.SubsidiaryName


Update tr
Set tr.ContactsSameSegmentFromLastWave = t.PreviousSample
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.Temp1 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname


Update dbo.TempReport 
Set Perc_ContactsSameSegmentFromLastWave = CAST((CAST(ContactsSameSegmentFromLastWave AS numeric(10,2))/CAST(PreviousWaveSampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(6,4))
WHERE ContactsSameSegmentFromLastWave <> 0 and ContactsSameSegmentFromLastWave is not null and PreviousWaveSampleCount <> 0


DROP TABLE dbo.Temp1

--% of Contacts from last wave under different Segment
--33 sec
IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'Temp2' and type = 'U')
DROP TABLE dbo.Temp2


select S.GrslistId,G.SubsidiaryName,COUNT(1) AS PreviousSample into dbo.Temp2 from dbo.CPERM_Prev_Sample G with(nolock)
INNER JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_GRSList] L with(nolock)
ON G.CPERMListid = L.GRSListId
INNER JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[vw_Mst_Geography] Geo with(nolock)
ON G.SubsidiaryName = Geo.SubsidiaryName
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Scorecard] S with(nolock)
ON G.CPERMListid != S.GrslistId AND Geo.SubsidiaryId = ISNULL(S.SubsidiaryId,0) AND G.Contactid = S.ContactNumber
WHERE S.RejectionCount = 0 and 1=1----Need to ask
GROUP BY S.GrslistId,G.SubsidiaryName

Set tr.ContactsDifferentSegmentFromLastWave = t.PreviousSample
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.Temp2 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname


Update dbo.TempReport 
Set Perc_ContactsDifferentSegmentFromLastWave = CAST((CAST(ContactsDifferentSegmentFromLastWave AS numeric(10,2))/CAST(PreviousWaveSampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(5,4))
WHERE ContactsDifferentSegmentFromLastWave <> 0 and ContactsDifferentSegmentFromLastWave is not null and PreviousWaveSampleCount <> 0

INNER JOIN [vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[SubsidiaryDetails] Geo with(nolock)
ON S.SubsidiaryID = Geo.SubsidiaryID
WHERE S.ContactNumber in 
(Select distinct S.ContactNumber from [dbo].[Scorecard] S with(nolock)
LEFT JOIN CPERM_Prev_Sample G with(nolock)
ON S.ContactNumber = G.Contactid
WHERE G.ContactId is null AND S.RejectionCount = 0) and 1=1
GROUP BY S.GrslistId,Geo.SubsidiaryName


Update tr
Set tr.NewContactInThisWave = t.ContactCount
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.Temp3 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname


Update dbo.TempReport 
Set Perc_NewContactInThisWave = CAST((CAST(NewContactInThisWave AS numeric(12,4))/CAST(SampleCount AS numeric(12,4))) AS numeric(7,4))
WHERE NewContactInThisWave <> 0 and SampleCount <> 0 and NewContactInThisWave is not null


DROP TABLE dbo.Temp3

--% Managed Contacts  from last wave
--1 sec
IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'Temp4' and type = 'U')
DROP TABLE dbo.Temp4


Select CPERMListid AS GRSListId,SubsidiaryName,Count(1) AS ManagedContact into dbo.Temp4 from dbo.CPERM_Prev_Sample G with(nolock)
WHERE ISNULL(t_a1_ManagedContact,0) = 1 and 1=1
GROUP BY CPERMListid,SubsidiaryName


Update tr
Set tr.ManagedContactsFromLastWave = t.ManagedContact
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.Temp4 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname


Update dbo.TempReport 
Set ManagedContactsDifferenceFromLastWave = ManagedContact - ManagedContactsFromLastWave
WHERE ManagedContactsFromLastWave is not null


Update dbo.TempReport 
Set Perc_ManagedContactsDifferenceFromLastWave = CAST((CAST(ManagedContactsDifferenceFromLastWave AS numeric(10,2))/CAST(PreviousWaveSampleCount AS numeric(10,2))) AS numeric(6,4))
WHERE ManagedContactsDifferenceFromLastWave <> 0 and PreviousWaveSampleCount <> 0 and ManagedContactsDifferenceFromLastWave is not null
GO

--% Sample  from Previous Wave
--
IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'Temp5' and type = 'U')
DROP TABLE dbo.Temp5


Select CPERMListid AS GRSListId,SubsidiaryName,Count(1) AS SampleCount into dbo.Temp5 from dbo.CPERM_Prev_Sample G with(nolock)
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY CPERMListid,SubsidiaryName


Update tr
Set tr.PreviousWaveSampleCount = t.SampleCount
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.Temp5 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname


Update tr
Set tr.DifferenceFromPreviousWave = tr.SampleCount - tr.PreviousWaveSampleCount
from dbo.TempReport tr

Update tr
Set tr.IntendedCompletes = ISNULL(t.Lookup_Interview_Target,0)
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN [dbo].[SRC_InterviewTarget_new] t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.level4
WHERE t.Grslistid not in (13,32,35,36,24,25)


--Previous Wave Data Quality

Update tr
Set tr.PreviousWaveFixableRejectionCount = ISNULL(t.FixableRejection,0)
from dbo.TempReport tr 
INNER JOIN dbo.DataQuality_FY18Q1 t with(nolock)
ON tr.grslistid = t.grslistid and tr.subsidiaryname = t.subsidiaryname
